name: D 21-10-4
description:
Digital collage made on October 4, 2021.

I made this collage while at work. While waiting for feedback, I add objects one by one using Photoshop.

This collage more or less illustrates the process of my work at that time, waiting from one person that was also waiting for another. I can only wait and suddenly Whatsapp cannot be used because the Facebook server is down. Yay for a while, let's have a rest.
